{"tid":806682,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真無得揀）p記8mb寬頻求救/心得","createTime":"2018-09-05T01:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T02:22:59.000Z","uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2727d74c19907d53637282baba46ae3aedc94bf0","tid":806682,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"上網search左好多個網伏到喊<br />\n1. $298一個月實際6-7mb下載1mb上載<br />\n2.一個月點都會斷1/2次線<br />\n3.睇片（1部機）1080p都要load，（2部機）會斷/降480p，如加上電話咪....<br />\n4. 打機有啲講唔大影響睇ping，但有啲就話唔洗再諗打機。<br />\n咁係咪steam下載隻game會仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住就見好多人推--4g sim-card router<br />\n好處-相對快好多平均上下載有50-100mb<br />\n但係呢<br />\n壞處-睇區同睇咩台，有啲訊號差會好唔穩定<br />\n特別係夜晚個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無限plan 5gb後限速（睇幾套劇就仆街）<br />\n有啲話限速都快過個寬頻，但我而家3無限爆左<br />\n（多人）youtube 連load都唔得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n用過p記會轉用sim card router<br />\n但有部分人用完覺得好唔穩定又轉返用p記<br />\n有無爸打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願比p記撚狗咁撚硬食，定係試下博sim card router？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：得返2個月 $178 bb1000命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉"},{"pid":"4811087dca388c54315c9510848b878a14ed4401","tid":806682,"uid":178520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef0d94084fb260f0ddc63fff36efb50112c66534","tid":806682,"uid":198879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}